{"root":{"data":{"id":"dgwgnhp6hig0","created":1772877582266,"text":"高一地理必修二"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgwgnuxyl680","created":1772877611095,"text":"第一章：人口"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgwgreijxeo0","created":1772877888791,"text":"世界人口分布"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgwgrh7i1nk0","created":1772877894653,"text":"四大稠密区：东亚、南亚、欧洲西部、北美东部","layout_right_offset":{"x":25,"y":-1}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgwgrlpwoiw0","created":1772877904473,"text":"明显稀疏区：高纬度、干旱沙漠、湿热雨林、高山高原"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgwgrrfuv800","created":1772877916926,"text":"影响分布的因素"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgwgrwp9ipk0","created":1772877928379,"text":"自然因素：气候（温和）、地形（平原）、水源、土壤、矿产资源"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgwgry7ydy00","created":1772877931686,"text":"人文因素：开发历史、经济发展水平（就业）、交通、政策"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgwgs62jcoo0","created":1772877948773,"text":"南半球人口较少的原因：陆地面积小，多海洋性气候（温带气候区陆地少）"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}